description:
Below Deck - Season 1, Episode 3



Dude, That's a Dude, Dude

The charter guests are five single men, who set out on a mission to pick up women with help from Dave and Eddie. Meanwhile, Dave's birthday is celebrated; Adrienne, Kat and Sam continue to clash; and Sam and C.J. flirt.



Original Air Date: 15-Jul-2013




NOTE: This is the missing episode that was banned in the US and was never shown.


Also, this file is only 38:14 minutes long. So, I believe that the scene that got this episode banned was edited out of this rebroadcast
